{"tid":1921954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「宣傳戰嚟啦」人哋有大外宣，我哋都有戰略","createTime":"2020-03-12T09:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T13:14:21.000Z","uid":296370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"09bd1245b6275b96ee613165e20b886a40500ec8","tid":1921954,"uid":296370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:22:13.000Z","msg":"之前係兩個熱門Post comment過，依家獨立成Post<br />\n大家要帶頭圍堵中共，要做到以下依幾步<br />\n1:係Twitter 分享防疫心得俾外國人<br />\n2:進階地整英文文宣，講述香港人的防疫工作點有效率（重點係solidarity)同埋有咩困難（柒婆唔封關，妖魔化罷工嘅醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯etc)<br />\n3:聯合台灣人，輸出台灣-香港抗疫模式，拆鳩細衛大台，講解台灣點咁成功阻止疫情蔓延。簡而言之即係：疫症當前，政府強硬救之，若不言，人民自救之。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4:將矛頭指向中共，指責pandemic 嘅出現係因為中共世衛合謀，阻礙真實資訊流通。<br />\n以下本人列出三點要求<br />\n4.1:習近平必須向世界道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.2:中國必須向世界所有受影響國家賠償，各國應聯合追討<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.3:譚德塞應立刻因抗疫不力而解除職務，然後提出要求重組世衛，調查世衞內部的勾結情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5:聯合世界排華力量，要令人盡可能唔排擠自己就必須要人識分中國定香港人，而依一點就係由政見立埸去分，先由用廣東話講「天滅中共，全黨死清光，電腦大爆炸」（生鬼D)開始，因為藍絲D死仆街多數唔撚注意衛生，仲要同外國小粉紅同出一轍散播美國播毒陰謀論，要放大政治立場決定文明程度、衛生程度依一點，形成「反共者就即係有高度衛生意識，有同理心同有人文關懷」的觀念邏輯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6:最後就係要教曉世界信「共產黨一成，焦土即迎」的教訓，中共=唔可信，毫無底線，世界應不再忍讓或妥協，應採取強硬政策回應中國，保護自由、民主等任何一個地方要建全運行都需要嘅核心價值，帶出Free Hong Kong嘅主旨（仲有Tibet,新彊等）<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有用就share啦，已經唔長㗎啦！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EpTpRae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpTpRae.png&h=f8600713&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bcnuhQf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbcnuhQf.png&h=0922b8f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b61OyoC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb61OyoC.gif&h=12ebfe8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOdpRai.gi